{"tid":2369462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"按摩槍增速 狂Click搶茅台","createTime":"2021-01-17T07:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T10:33:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d904c1f9b48622c4f0cf774026187e32e360965a","tid":2369462,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210117/WZFF56DQWVH6RHJITLGOJLDOYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210117%2FWZFF56DQWVH6RHJITLGOJLDOYQ%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=00335787\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210117%2FWZFF56DQWVH6RHJITLGOJLDOYQ%2F&h=11dba3ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210117/WZFF56DQWVH6RHJITLGOJLDOYQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n按摩槍增速 狂Click搶茅台<br />\n<br />\n國酒貴州茅台的炒價居高不止，近期掀起網上搶購潮。有內地網民不惜利用按摩槍加快手速，在手機上狂按購買掣搶購茅台（圖），片段曝光後，引來不少人仿效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n炒賣每支賺2,400元<br />\n<br />\n據資料顯示，每年約有883萬瓶平價茅台投入市場，網上售價約為每瓶1,500元人民幣（下同，約1,820港元），但炒價可升至3,500元（約4,247港元），茅。。。。。。。。。。。。同時記錄每瓶出售茅台流向，以保價格穩定。<br />\n<br />\n有網民建議：「購買茅台的人須登記身份證，每個身份證一年只能買一次。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aMdM2MncFDB73h3CQ50ak9hEyH4=/751x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CQSHWB56DFHMVK7JNIBAZ2M474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaMdM2MncFDB73h3CQ50ak9hEyH4%3D%2F751x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCQSHWB56DFHMVK7JNIBAZ2M474.jpg&h=27861b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微博"},{"pid":"33a9328ae53e54e063726ad4ed2597e012000d62","tid":2369462,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"屌裝枝stylus啦<br />\n使撚用自己手指"},{"pid":"f0e88fe16f1ad1315af4ea4ac73d797f61126efc","tid":2369462,